    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Check out this absolute beauty. Honestly, it's basically showroom quality\u2014I've babied it since day one and it looks incredible. You won't find a scratch on it! It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
