      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and all interior surfaces are free of wear. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with factory precision. Accompanied by a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists, this vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, reflecting meticulous ownership and a total absence of wear. Every surface and component remains in a pristine state, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this masterfully preserved investment.",
      "price": 46500.0,
