      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just a pristine ride waiting for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
