      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in pristine, factory-original condition. This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six, mated to the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the four-wheel independent double-wishbone suspension. The engine bay is a time capsule, retaining all OEM vacuum lines and heat shielding with no aftermarket modifications. This example exhibits flawless panel fitment, zero undercarriage oxidation, and a cockpit that remains in showroom state. A rare opportunity to own a mechanically perfect icon of the Golden Era of Japanese performance.",
